<p>Opening a Torah today, you will be presented with modern Hebrew script:</p>
<blockquote class="blockquote">
<p>בראשית ברא אלהים את השמים ואת הארץ</p>
</blockquote>
<p>Using only the Latin script that English speakers are familiar with this might read something like the following:</p>
<blockquote class="blockquote">
<p>BRASYT BRA ALHYM AT HSMYM VAT HARZ</p>
</blockquote>
