<section id="procedure" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="procedure">Procedure</h2>
<ol type="1">
<li>Split the verse into words.</li>
<li>Join the words into a string of letters</li>
<li>Multiply the number of letters and the values of each of the letters to calculate the numerator.</li>
<li>Multiply the number of words and the sum of the values of the letters of each word to calculate the denominator.</li>
<li>The ratio of the numerator / denominator is <strong>an accurate approximation of <img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?%5Cpi"></strong>.</li>
</ol>
